{
  "texts": [
    "If we want to define context awareness in relation to IoT we can refer to it as the proficiency of devices to apprehend and adjust to their milieu by assimilating pertinent and relevant contextual data [19].",
    "This encompasses factors, such as location, temporal aspects, user behaviour, environmental parameters, and device characteristics [20].",
    "Through the amalgamation of context-awareness, IoT systems can render more significant and meaningful interactions, thereby augmenting user experiences and optimizing resource deployment.",
    "A primary impetus for CA systems in IoT is the burgeoning intricacy and heterogeneity of devices and the data they engender.",
    "As the proliferation of IoT devices and sensors escalates, the magnitude of data they generate becomes overwhelming."
  ]
}